<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men yào zàn měi nǐ wǒ zhǔ 迦南920</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yào zàn měi nǐ, wǒ zhǔ. wǒ men yào zàn měi nǐ wǒ zhǔ.
 yīn wèi nǐ gěi wǒ men chéng jiù le dà shì. wǒ men yào xiàng nǐ huān hū.
 zài wú bié shén néng xiàng nǐ, zài wú bié shén néng xiàng nǐ.
 nǐ mǎn yǒu cí ài, nǐ mǎn yǒu lián mǐn, wéi yǒu nǐ shì zhēn huó shén.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>920</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>